<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>每日三理 · Theoria</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
{% import "_card.html.j2" as card %}

<header class="site-header">
  <div class="wrap header-inner">
    <div class="brand"><h1>每日三理</h1><span class="en">Theoria</span></div>
    <nav class="nav">
      <a href="index.html" class="active">今日</a>
      <a href="archive.html">歷史</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="wrap">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="date">{{ date_str }}</div>
    <div class="lead">每天三個可應用的學術理論。第 1 天就是一篇完整、夠深的文章；第 2、3 天再往更深推。每個分段都把話講透、並配上具體例子。外加一張回想卡，複習更早學過的。</div>
    <div class="cycle">
      <span>本輪進度</span>
      <span class="cycle-dots">
        {% for d in [1,2,3] %}<span class="dot{% if d < active_day %} filled{% elif d == active_day %} filled current{% endif %}"></span>{% endfor %}
      </span>
      <span>第 {{ active_day }} 天 / 3 · {{ hero_focus }}</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  {% if pool_notice %}<div class="pool-warn {{ pool_notice.level }}">{{ '⚠️' if pool_notice.level == 'crit' else '🔻' }} {{ pool_notice.text }}</div>{% endif %}

  <div class="section-eyebrow">今日主題</div>

  {% for t in theories %}
  {{ card.card(t, active_day) }}
  {% endfor %}

  {% if reviews %}
  <div class="section-eyebrow">今日回想卡 · 複習更早學過的</div>
  {% for r in reviews %}
  <div class="review-card">
    <div class="review-top"><span class="tag tag--{{ r.domain_class }}">{{ r.domain_short }}</span><span>複習 · 距上次 {{ r.distance_days }} 天</span></div>
    <div class="review-q"><span class="name">{{ r.name_zh }}</span>　{{ r.question }}</div>
    <div class="review-due">📅 排程：完成於 {{ r.completed_str }}，第 {{ r.nth }} 次複習到期</div>
    <button class="reveal-btn">顯示答案</button>
    <div class="review-a">
      <div class="prose"><p>{{ r.answer }}</p>{{ card.eg(r.answer_example) }}</div>
      <div class="mnemonic">🔑 <b>{{ r.mnemonic }}</b></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
  {% endif %}

  {% if note %}<div class="note">{{ note }}</div>{% endif %}

</main>

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="wrap">
    每日三理 · Theoria。第 1 天完整入門、第 2、3 天往更深推、每段都把話講透並配例子 ＋ 間隔回想複習。<br>
    內容由 AI 每日生成、停在概念層級以求準確；不引用無法查證的具體研究數字。{% if generated_at %}　更新於 {{ generated_at }}。{% endif %}
  </div>
</footer>

<script src="assets/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
